; A. Description
;    A list of commands here configures timer6 and generates a period interrupt.
;
; B. Preparation
;    N/A
;
; C. Prerequisite Example (abov_example_config.h)
;    1. Timer6
;
; For more information, read a user's manual of the target device carefully.
;
; Timer60
; 1. Channel                   : 0 (Timer60)
;
; 2. Config                    : [ 0 i 2 ]
;    Operation                 : i (Interrupt)
;    Data                      : 2
;
; Timer60
sendln 'cm timer6'
mpause 30
sendln 'uninit 0'
mpause 30
sendln 'init 0'
mpause 30
sendln 'config 0 i 2'
mpause 30
sendln 'log on'
mpause 30
sendln 'start 0'
